Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.97,0:22:36.34,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明毫无定所
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.66,0:22:38.94,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却隐藏起寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.34,0:22:41.68,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探索着前进
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.93,0:22:44.06,OP_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不在的夜晚
